{"tid":2138612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反cup] [美國大選] 最新民調顯示，川普在關鍵州領先","createTime":"2020-08-03T16:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T17:52:02.000Z","uid":52658,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a370e270e3596bedbf902f4531f4ff89ed17d6b","tid":2138612,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"由英國每日快報（立場偏向右派）揭露、<br />\n<br />\n委由 Democracy Institute / Sunday Express 做的民調，<br />\n<br />\n顯示川普在關鍵州 Florida, Iowa, Michigan, Minnesota, Pennsylvania<br />\n<br />\n和 Wisconsin 的民調以 48% 的平均支持度領先拜登的 43%，<br />\n<br />\n讓川普的預測選舉人票數來到 309，對比於拜登的 229，<br />\n<br />\n雖然部分各別關鍵州的民調差距是在誤差值範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n這應該是近期川普第一次在民調中領先拜登。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補充一下全國支持度：<br />\n<br />\n川普 : 拜登 = 48% : 46%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白人支持度：<br />\n<br />\n川普 : 拜登 = 53% : 46%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑人支持度：<br />\n<br />\n川普 : 拜登 = 20% : 77%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西班牙裔支持度：<br />\n<br />\n川普 : 拜登 = 38% : 51%<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1596417488.A.F3A.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1596417488.A.F3A.html&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=ca6bd3c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1596417488.A.F3A.html</a>"},{"pid":"23e9041bc965ca1e9918eae7e93c372cd295629d","tid":2138612,"uid":300956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"testing"},{"pid":"695ee0ffe1d7ff03d7936157ad47909240f8512d","tid":2138612,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5bd2d33544af72eaa6e3cbd42a4d688f392450f","tid":2138612,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"Donald trump加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa